# CC2650 Datasheet
  Microcontroller
    - ARM Cortex -M3 (32bit CPU)
    - 128KB of In-System Programmable Flash
    - 8KB of SRAM for Cache
    - 20KB of Ultralow-Leakage SRAM
    - Supports OTA ( Over-The-Air) Upgrade
    
  Peripherals
    - 12-Bit ADC
    - UART
    - 2x SSI(SPI, MICROWIRE, TI)
    - I2C
    - I2S
    - Real-Time Clock
    - 10, 15, 31 GPIOs
    
  Power Management
  MODE                  Software configureable Power Modes            Reset pin held
                        Active     IDLE       STANDBY      SHUTDOWN
                  
  CPU                   Active     Off        Off          Off
  Flash                 On         Available  Off          Off
  SRAM                  On         On         On           Off
  Radio                 Available  Available  Off          Off
  Supply System         On         On         Duty Cycled  Off
  Wake up on RTC        Available  Available  Available    Off
  Wake up on Pin Edge   Available  Available  Available    Available
  Wake up on Reset Pin  Available  Available  Available    Available
  
